('junior', 'The more you practice, ___ you become.', '["A. the more fluently", "B. the more fluent", "C. more fluent", "D. most fluent"]'::jsonb, 'B', 1, 'the more... the more 平行結構。'),
('junior', 'He speaks English ___ a native speaker.', '["A. as fluent as", "B. as fluently as", "C. so fluent as", "D. more fluent than"]'::jsonb, 'B', 1, '修飾動詞 speaks 用副詞比較 as fluently as。'),
