('professor', 'Metonymy is exemplified by ___.', '["A. ''kick the bucket''", "B. The crown announced...", "C. It''s raining cats and dogs", "D. Time flies"]'::jsonb, 'B', 1, 'The crown 借代王室為 metonymy。'),
